one of our clients' locations worldwide.

295
00:21:42,342 --> 00:21:44,468
Strategy packets
will be shipped in advance.

296
00:21:44,553 --> 00:21:45,553
Ned would be given a seat

297
00:21:45,637 --> 00:21:48,556
and find one of our transition specialists
waiting for him.

298
00:21:49,683 --> 00:21:52,560
Mr. Laskin, the reason
we're having this conversation

299
00:21:52,644 --> 00:21:54,729
is your position is no longer available.

300
00:21:54,813 --> 00:21:57,064
