301
00:21:57,149 --> 00:21:59,483
Hearing the words "you've been let go"
is never easy.

302
00:21:59,568 --> 00:22:01,986
Change is always scary,
but consider the following.

303
00:22:02,070 --> 00:22:04,322
Anybody who ever built an empire
or changed the world

304
00:22:04,406 --> 00:22:05,489
sat where you are now.

305
00:22:05,574 --> 00:22:08,576
