365
00:24:40,896 --> 00:24:43,481
Mr. Gregory hired me,
he's the only one who can fire me.

366
00:24:43,565 --> 00:24:45,608
You know what?
I'm gonna go talk to him.

367
00:24:46,193 --> 00:24:48,027
- Mr. Bingham.
- No, no, no. You can't follow me.

368
00:24:48,111 --> 00:24:49,487
You're on a computer screen,
